本期圆桌，让我们一起面对它 ：）</div><div class="actions"><button class="button-link share pull-left" data-id="284" data-token="fenkai"><i class="fi fi-share"></i>分享</button><span class="visits text-muted">85878441 次浏览 </span><span class="bull">&bull;</span><a href="/roundtable/fenkai/followers" class="followers text-muted"><span class="count" data-count="4571"> 4571</span> 人关注</a></div></div></div><div class="module"><ul class="menu-nav horizontal"><li ><a href="/roundtable/fenkai">48 <span class="nowrap">条动态</span></a></li><li ><a href="/roundtable/fenkai/questions">34 <span class="nowrap">个问题</span></a></li><li ><a href="/roundtable/fenkai/comments">98 <span class="nowrap">条讨论</span></a></li></ul></div><div class="feeds loose user-answers"><ul class="items" data-paging><li class="item" data-type="Answer"><a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-107421536"></a><link itemprop="url" href="/question/22977715/answer/425439106"><meta itemprop="question-id" content="1371900"><meta itemprop="question-url-token" content="22977715"><meta itemprop="answer-id" content="107421536"><meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="425439106"><div class="item-header"><h2 class="item-title"><a class="js-title-link" target="_blank" href="/question/22977715/answer/425439106">你认为离别时最伤感的话或者诗句是什么？</a></h2></div><article class="entry answer"><div class="entry-left hidden-phone"><a class="rating hidden-expanded js-expand js-vote-count" data-bind-votecount>1637</a><div class="votebar visible-expanded"><button class="up " title="赞同"><i class="fi-voteup-arrow"></i><span class="count">1637</span><span class="sr-only">赞同</span></button><button class="down" title="反对，不会显示你的姓名"><i class="fi-votedown-arrow"></i><span class="sr-only">反对，不会显示你的姓名</span></button></div></div><div class="entry-body"><div class="entry-meta"><strong class="author-line"><a class="author" href="/people/xiao-shi-9" data-hovercard='p$t$xiao-shi-9'>灯下说书人</a>，<span title="街边远行客，灯下说书人" class="bio">街边远行客，灯下说书人</span></strong></div><div class="entry-content js-collapse-body" data-author-name="灯下说书人" data-entry-url="/question/22977715/answer/425439106"><div class="summary hidden-expanded js-expand">「明日隔山岳，世事两茫茫。」 出自杜甫《赠卫八处士》，全诗如下： 人生不相见，动如参与商。今夕复何夕，共此灯烛光。少壮能几时，鬓发各已苍。访旧半为鬼，惊呼热中肠。焉知二十载，重上君子堂。昔别君未婚，儿女忽成行。怡然敬父执，问我来何方。问答乃…<a class="toggle-expand inline" href="/question/22977715/answer/425439106">显示全部</a></div><div class="visible-expanded"><div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="1637"><span class="voters"><span class="member"><a href="/people/zhi-zheng-sen" data-hovercard='p$t$zhi-zheng-sen'>惊蛰</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/finalwind1" data-hovercard='p$t$finalwind1'>Trivial.573</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/yi-du-34-93" data-hovercard='p$t$yi-du-34-93'>曳渡</a></span></span> <a class="more">等人赞同</a></div><script type="text" class="content"><p>「明日隔山岳，世事两茫茫。」</p><p><br></p><p>出自杜甫《赠卫八处士》，全诗如下：</p><p><br></p><p>人生不相见，动如参与商。</p><p>今夕复何夕，共此灯烛光。</p><p>少壮能几时，鬓发各已苍。</p><p>访旧半为鬼，惊呼热中肠。</p><p>焉知二十载，重上君子堂。</p><p>昔别君未婚，儿女忽成行。</p><p>怡然敬父执，问我来何方。</p><p>问答乃未已，驱儿罗酒浆。</p><p>夜雨剪春韭，新炊间黄粱。</p><p>主称会面难，一举累十觞。</p><p>十觞亦不醉，感子故意长。</p><p>明日隔山岳，世事两茫茫。</p><p><br></p><p>少时读诗，读到过这一首，当时一知半解，并不能真正体会其中的含义，年岁渐长，经历了很多分别，才慢慢懂了诗里无可奈何的悲伤。</p><p>最近整理旧物，翻到奶奶中学毕业时的纪念册，留下笔墨和照片的人们不是近百岁就是已经辞世。隔着时光和被蠹虫咬出的孔洞都能感受到一种郑重。奶奶给我讲过当年她作为女生班长奔走校园找老师校长题词的旧事，仿佛能透过纪念册里那张勤恳而热切的少女脸庞看到当年的场景。</p><p>（多图预警）</p><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-24ee32dd63a282a66ff1f4ad07415b12_b.jpg" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="3264" data-rawheight="2448" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-4fa676a0dccfd6034d49f91646736a66_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="3264" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-24ee32dd63a282a66ff1f4ad07415b12_r.jpg"><figcaption>初中毕业纪念册 封面为手绣</figcaption></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-47441c5c46c0f3931cd6bc25dc803d41_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="2448" data-rawheight="3264" data-default-wat